  "detailed_description": "Cyberstalking game <i><strong>Pricolage -IDOLIZED-</strong></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510890/extras/c42f5187492d5d33d2444186775e5670.avif?t=1735976924\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>Cyberstalk the popular K-pop idol!<br>Pricolage -IDOLIZED- is a short adventure game in which you search around an Instagram-like social media platform for traces of Sena–a K-pop idol at the height of fame–after her disappearance. Wander through an ocean of darkness and greed–the internet–in order to locate her!<br><br><br>■Use posts to find out what people are up to in their offline lives!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510890/extras/5cf795ff6d4dab19bc3e2e71db3f32c2.poster.avif?t=1735976924\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510890/extras/5cf795ff6d4dab19bc3e2e71db3f32c2.webm?t=1735976924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510890/extras/5cf795ff6d4dab19bc3e2e71db3f32c2.mp4?t=1735976924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Follow your To-Do List and click on anything on-screen that catches your eye to obtain search words.<br><br><br><br>■The internet knows all!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510890/extras/6d2aa4220c2fa836e08012c51a7c55b3.poster.avif?t=1735976924\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510890/extras/6d2aa4220c2fa836e08012c51a7c55b3.webm?t=1735976924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510890/extras/6d2aa4220c2fa836e08012c51a7c55b3.mp4?t=1735976924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use the search words you obtain to deduce Sena’s whereabouts.<br>Put your cyberstalking prowess to the test and see if you can uncover all the idol’s ins and outs.<br><br><br>■Gather evidence!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510890/extras/634aeba0863e5580e3065f1477c5fa96.poster.avif?t=1735976924\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510890/extras/634aeba0863e5580e3065f1477c5fa96.webm?t=1735976924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510890/extras/634aeba0863e5580e3065f1477c5fa96.mp4?t=1735976924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The pictures in Sena’s posts just might lead you to identifying a culprit. <br>Oh, but what’s this? A pic of Sena undressing? There are more important things to find…or are there? Gather any evidence of Sena’s whereabouts!<br><br><br>■Multiple endings!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510890/extras/3cfa31fa8c575aef10e0e6d9337cd7ab.poster.avif?t=1735976924\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510890/extras/3cfa31fa8c575aef10e0e6d9337cd7ab.webm?t=1735976924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510890/extras/3cfa31fa8c575aef10e0e6d9337cd7ab.mp4?t=1735976924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Scour the internet and perhaps you’ll find hidden endings. How things play out is up to you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character Introduction</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510890/extras/706938766136fe4cd004c7099f3cce13.avif?t=1735976924\" width=501 height=600 /></span><br><br>■セナ：<br>A member of the K-pop idol group 7uster who debuted after the audition television show Seven Angels. <br>Kind-hearted and hard-working, yet just a smidge naive. She became a K-pop idol to make her dream of bringing a smile to everyone’s face come true.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Is Sena happy...?</h2>Finding information from the internet filled with lies and deceit will be your path to the truth. <br>See through until the end with what happens with Sena.",
